org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.handler

Class VeluxBridgeHandler.BridgeParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.handler.VeluxBridgeHandler.BridgeParameters
  • Enclosing class:
    VeluxBridgeHandler

    @NonNullByDefault
public class VeluxBridgeHandler.BridgeParameters
extends java.lang.Object

    Set of information retrieved from the bridge/gateway:

    • actuators - Already known actuators,
    • scenes - Already on the gateway defined scenes,
    • gateway - Current status of the gateway status,
    • firmware - Information about the gateway firmware revision,
    • lanConfig - Information about the gateway configuration,
    • wlanConfig - Information about the gateway configuration.
